item.title: CVE-2010-5108|2024-08-07T04:09:38.941Z -- trac -- trac
item.description: Trac 0.11.6 does not properly check workflow permissions before modifying a ticket. This can be exploited by an attacker to change the status and resolution of tickets without having proper permissions.
